org.apache.hawq.pxf.api

Interface ReadResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvroResolver, HBaseResolver, HiveColumnarSerdeResolver, HiveResolver, HiveStringPassResolver, StringPassResolver, WritableResolver

    public interface ReadResolver
    Interface that defines the deserialization of one record brought from the ReadAccessor. All deserialization methods (e.g, Writable, Avro, ...) implement this interface.
